{"tid":1151331,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(年經/公投)你地究竟介唔介意另一半同ex有聯絡？","createTime":"2019-05-12T13:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T16:37:46.000Z","uid":246108,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e584373e4b7e8c439fa010eb031143957f518547","tid":1151331,"uid":246108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"想知道大家既睇法<br />\n<br />\n所指既聯絡唔包括有flirt/曖昧既情況出現<br />\n只當係普通朋友咁閒聊 問候下 share下啲近況/好笑野etc.<br />\n<br />\n我個人係覺得如非必要都唔希望另一半同ex仲有聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分左手唔係一定就要變成仇人 block哂對方所有野<br />\n但亦無必要聯絡呀唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話哂都曾經係最親密最貼近既人 邊個會想另一半同一個咁樣身份既人仲有來往<br />\n<br />\n或者單身既時候無乜所謂 當有拍拖既時候係咪應該避忌下<br />\n<br />\n係咪我太痴線妒忌心太重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 介意/唔應該聯絡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔介意/可以聯絡"},{"pid":"c2429e6bbb37cb720054fab3efa991b08ce0c791","tid":1151331,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T13:12:21.000Z","msg":"有聯絡咪得閒打場友誼波囉<br />\n反正條撚平時都入開架啦<br />\n屌足幾年果d 你直頭屌緊人地碌撚既倒模閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4361d4e82b22b2bdfa66a809a80897a7eab00b69","tid":1151331,"uid":246108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c2429e6bbb37cb720054fab3efa991b08ce0c791","tid":1151331,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T13:12:21.000Z","msg":"有聯絡咪得閒打場友誼波囉<br />\n反正條撚平時都入開架啦<br />\n屌足幾年果d 你直頭屌緊人地碌撚既倒模閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T13:58:10.000Z","msg":"又未到呢個地步既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係覺得佢地會搞反埋一齊<br />\n只係覺得有必要日常生活要聯絡姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6dc66cf61dacba